<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>و <span style="color:#950000">" كَبكَبُ "</span>: اسْم جَبَل، غير منصرف.<span style="color:#006d98"> وَأنْشد:</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span style="color:#008000">(وَمَنْ يغترب عَن قَوْمِه لَا يَزَلْ يَرَى ... مَصارعَ مظلوم مَجَرَّا ومَسْحَبَا)</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span style="color:#008000">(وتُدْفَنُ مِنْهُ الطالحاتُ وَمَنْ يُسئ ... يَكُنْ مَا أساءَ النَّارَ فِي رَأس كَبْكَبَا)</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>و<span style="color:#950000">" شَعُوبُ "</span>: اسْم للمنية، غير منصرف.<span style="color:#006d98"> وَأما قَوْله:</span><a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span style="color:#008000">(وكل فَتَى سَتَشْعَبُهُ شَعُوٌب ... وإِنْ أثْرَى وإنْ لَاقى فَلَاحَا)</span><a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>فَإِنَّمَا صَرَفَهُ للضَّرُورَة.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>و<span style="color:#950000">" المَنْجَنُون "</span>: الدَّاليَة، مُؤَنّثَة.<span style="color:#006d98"> وَأنْشد:</span><a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span style="color:#008000">( ... ... ... ... ... هَل الدَّهرُ إِلَّا مَنْجنَوُنٌ تَقَلَّبُ)</span><a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>و<span style="color:#950000">" المَنْجَنِيقُ "</span>: مُؤَنّثَة.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>و<span style="color:#950000">" مُوسَى "</span> الْحَدِيد مؤنثه،<span style="color:#006d98"> لقَولهم:</span> <span style="color:#950000">" مُوسَى خَذِمَة "</span>.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>و<span style="color:#950000">" السِّنّ "</span> مُؤَنّثَة.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>